{"tid":1305801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「九龍灣肥撕」連環13拳 捱打義工：如還手會傷途人","createTime":"2019-07-11T03:00:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T16:03:43.000Z","uid":68738,"like":63,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed1300585252238e48b32bce39c8a61ff93399d","tid":1305801,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:00:27.000Z","msg":"「連儂牆」遍地開花，九龍灣淘大花園通往觀塘道的橋底，被市民闢為「連儂牆」，兩邊牆身貼滿市民心聲的貼紙。凌晨零時許，一名身型肥胖姓黃46歲男子到來，撕毀牆上的貼紙，姓李65歲老翁及姓麥36歲義工阻止時，黃先揮拳向李襲擊，並向麥粗言辱罵，「你搞革命，搞乜x嘢革命」，他並指住貼紙，「呢啲乜x嘢嚟㗎，後生仔唔係咁做嘢」。<br />\n<br />\n黃隨即動手向麥拳毆，將麥毆至倒地，麥起身與他理論，黃又問他有無養過家，「有冇煮過飯、有冇洗過碗？」麥答有，黃又聲稱飲醉酒，「我做乜都得，拮你兩刀都仲得」，短短分半鐘左右，麥被拳擊13次。<br />\n<br />\n現場片段所見，黃拳拳到肉，盡往麥的面部打去，連自己手上的雨傘也飛掉地上；而麥一直將雙手放在身後，既不還手，也沒閃避，直至支持不住跌在地上。<br />\n<br />\n現場約有6名青年男女圍觀，但他們初時也沒有阻止，直至黃打第5拳，有人才喝叫：「夠喇！」<br />\n<br />\n黃亦反指各人持勢凌人：「你成棚人行埋嚟圍我，你報警我都報警。」警方其後到場，以涉嫌傷人拘捕黃，李及麥受傷送院。<br />\n<br />\n雖然「連儂牆」被撕毀，但事後多名義工即時修復，「連儂牆」回復原狀。<br />\n<br />\n麥經急症室醫生敷治後已經出院，回家休息。記者登門探訪，見他左邊嘴角和鎖骨位置敷了紗布，精神尚可。<br />\n<br />\n他指，該名男子破壞「連儂牆」的標貼，街坊阻止即被打，於是上前喝止。至於為何打不還手？麥說：「如果當時嘅環境還手，會令其他途人都受傷。」<br />\n<br />\n麥又指，對方並沒有出言挑釁，只是指罵在場人士「死廢青」，「我哋都冇撩佢」。麥不肯定對方是否真的飲醉酒。現時案件交由警方調查，不方便多提，以免影響司法程序。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190711/59810515\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810515&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnQWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=ddabcc3b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190711%2F59810515&h=739bd17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190711/59810515</a>"},{"pid":"7bf22e4ff879930d464ed6711bc918c863730e52","tid":1305801,"uid":522,"like":6,"dislike":9,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKMofAK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKMofAK.gif&h=caf841ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9be7e9feb6bbcf68bb8d86aa55d91c8e5a045bd8","tid":1305801,"uid":232751,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0S4w83m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0S4w83m.jpg&h=ad686a69&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0ad0ba456214ee808ccf2419f8a055b68fdd2d6","tid":1305801,"uid":25831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:01:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"098a534f2c7899e2a5a78d576380205cf22c6b91","tid":1305801,"uid":3194,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:02:45.000Z","msg":"唔還手都擋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔想再有人咁樣受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下次唔好咁傻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d92179cec72806335482bf3919e7a2ca2cfdec","tid":1305801,"uid":90883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:03:20.000Z","msg":"等天收"},{"pid":"690864689b233a5e50f9d302ee2879de7d8dcf1e","tid":1305801,"uid":54256,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"「拮你兩刀都仲得」<br />\n算唔算恐嚇？"},{"pid":"cd2dd8dd5aa4548a9a9116e3f7911f3f19c5b910","tid":1305801,"uid":107216,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"690864689b233a5e50f9d302ee2879de7d8dcf1e","tid":1305801,"uid":54256,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:13.000Z","msg":"「拮你兩刀都仲得」<br />\n算唔算恐嚇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"絕對係"},{"pid":"19f8e8e83eafab4524a8fcd673a2c09bd64cdaab","tid":1305801,"uid":54256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd2dd8dd5aa4548a9a9116e3f7911f3f19c5b910","tid":1305801,"uid":107216,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"690864689b233a5e50f9d302ee2879de7d8dcf1e","tid":1305801,"uid":54256,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"cit